          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-8-1685710655203-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-8-1685710655203-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-8-1685710655203-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fries are in the oven, chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> into quarters</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
